  "original_title": "QR \u0d9a\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0db8\u0dba \u0d85\u0db1\u0dd4\u0dc0 \u0d89\u0db1\u0dca\u0db0\u0db1 \u0db1\u0dd2\u0d9a\u0dd4\u0dad\u0dca \u0d9a\u0dbb\u0db1 \u0d89\u0db1\u0dca\u0db0\u0db1\u0dc4\u0dbd\u0dca \u0dc0\u0dd9\u0dad \u0db4\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0db8\u0dd4\u0d9b\u0dad\u0dcf\u0dc0",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Priority to petrol stations dispensing fuel as per QR system",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Ministry of Electricity and Energy says that the National Fuel License System (QR) will be implemented from tomorrow and all other systems including the system of issuing fuel based on the last number of the token and vehicle number plate will be completed after tomorrow.",
        "Also, the ministry said in a statement that priority will be given in issuing fuel to fuel stations that issue fuel according to the national fuel license system."
      ],
